X` | `MIX_COMPLETE` |\\n| `BUILDING_CONSTRUCT` | `BUILDING_CONSTRUCT` |\\n| `BUI
LDING_UPGRADE` | `BUILDING_UPGRADE` |\\n| `ASSET_GAIN` | `ASSET_GAIN_DAOYUN` |\\
n| `MARKET_TRADE` | `MARKET_TRADE` |\\n| `MARKET_LISTING` | `MARKET_LISTING` |\\
n\\n## 代码映射\\n\\n### API 层\\n\\n- `api/new-world-api/v1/quest.proto` — Ques
t 服务定义\\n- `api/shared/v1/configs/quest_configs.proto` — 任务配置定义\\n- `a
pi/shared/v1/configs/quest_reward_configs.proto` — 任务奖励配置定义\\n\\n### Biz
